 is the funniest shit I have read.  I want to party at your house.<br><br><br><i><b>Striiper</b> says:</i><br><br>Dude that is the funniest shit I have read.  I want to party at your house.<br><br><br><i><b>Vunstar/Lokkii</b> says:</i><br><br>one word...Tequilla<br><br><br><i><b>Anonymous</b> says:</i><br><br>4/ 211 steel reserve 16oz with 3oz shots 
